This map was tested, i fixed the bugs, works fine now, myself and daz made this map, and enjoyed it quite alot i must say, i recived alot of help from mappers at solidsurf, thanks to you guys! :D 

this is a skill map, i hope alot of people will enjoy it, its not as hard as other surf maps, although id class it was possibly a medium lvled skill map.

the jail is a fun jail, with rifles, and 2 separate bases in which each team can fire at each other, i thought this would be a good jail because i know when i go to jail i hate just dieing, so i put in kinda an aim map, not as big as an aim map, but good fun i think.
